<section class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>FAQS</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>WHAT IS INDOOR DIGITAL SIGNAGE ADVERTISING?</h3>
        <p>
          It's the placement of your ads on TV screens located inside high-traffic venues, 
          offering brand visibility where people are already engaged.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>DO YOU OFFER PACKAGES THAT INCLUDE SCREENS AND ONLINE ADS?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes! We offer bundled packages that combine <strong>indoor billboards</strong> with digital 
          marketing services like <strong>social ads</strong>, Google Ads, and SEO to maximize your reach 
          both online and offline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>CAN YOU HELP MY BUSINESS RANK ON GOOGLE?</h3>
        <p>
          Absolutely. We provide SEO services, Google Business setup, and local search 
          strategies to help your business show up when customers are searching for your 
          services in Denver.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    background: #F0EBD8 ;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    color: #000;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .faq-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .faq-card:last-child {
    grid-column: 1 / 2;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #000;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  p {
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .faq-card:last-child {
      grid-column: 1;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .faq-card {
      padding: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
